title: Off Camera With Sam Jones.Joseph Gordan Levitt.720p.HDTV_TTL
description:
http://offcamera.com/											

		Off Camera is a website, magazine, television show, and podcast.

Off Camera is hosted by photographer/director Sam Jones, who created the show out of his passion for 

the 

long form conversational interview, and as a way to share his conversations with a myriad of artists, 

actors, musicians, directors, skateboarders, photographers, and writers that pique his interest.	

TV Premiere  11-23-2015											

Grab the sample and check it out. 				

								

								

If you like it then go for it.					

Enjoy and and please share
